{"id":441702,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":28}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"177","ytitle":"","mtitle":"不能忘记!","ftitle":"","authors":["安珍"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"安珍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨，象一把火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着我；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同胞的尸体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在面前躺着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那凶手美国强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却得意的笑着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是为什么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是凭什么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人欺你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为你软弱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人欺你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为枪在他们手里拿着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，是人民的天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许，不许，绝对不许"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义强盗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再行凶作恶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻把枪口对准敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用枪来保卫和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫祖国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢侵略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让谁血洗土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赎罪恶!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633s021301.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>上海工人文化宫举办“阶级教育展览会”展品</FONT>"}]}